{"tid":2412883,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"尚悅‧天城獲批滿意紙 料下周開放現樓示範單位","createTime":"2021-02-18T09:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T16:02:26.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"17107cc3df119d4f429fcdf711ea445c74632227","tid":2412883,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:41:49.000Z","msg":"尚悅‧天城獲批滿意紙 料下周開放現樓示範單位<br />\n16:45 2021/02/18<br />\n<br />\n&quot;恒基物業代理有限公司營業(一)部總經理林達民指，唐人新村項目尚悅‧天城已獲批滿意紙，下星期會啟動銷售流程並開放現樓尚悅‧天城示範單位，有機會下周末將以招標發售。<br />\n<br />\n至於同系屯門青山灣新盤帝御‧嵐天(帝御第3期)加推價單6號共56伙，將於周六開售次輪128伙......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2880404/%E5%B0%9A%E6%82%A6%E2%80%A7%E5%A4%A9%E5%9F%8E%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9%E6%BB%BF%E6%84%8F%E7%B4%99%20%E6%96%99%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E7%8F%BE%E6%A8%93%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2880404%2F%25E5%25B0%259A%25E6%2582%25A6%25E2%2580%25A7%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25B4%2599%2520%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25AF%2584%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=4274b130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2880404/%E5%B0%9A%E6%82%A6%E2%80%A7%E5%A4%A9%E5%9F%8E%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9%E6%BB%BF%E6%84%8F%E7%B4%99%20%E6%96%99%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E7%8F%BE%E6%A8%93%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D?mtc=60037</a>"},{"pid":"613f30379d47666b07b177e2a4eba74d4f43afdb","tid":2412883,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"好隔涉下"},{"pid":"45a9b73f29e2a1eb86db2465e3ec3f586b58f507","tid":2412883,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-prox